main event: On 5 March 1966, two civilians observed a bright light that changed to green and descended on the horizon in Renton, Washington.
interesting points: The witnesses described the object as possibly resembling an aircraft but it gradually moved out of sight,No physical evidence was obtained from the sighting,The object produced a low humming sound,The witnesses perceived a significant size difference between the object and an airplane observed nearby,It was noted that loud noises accompanying the sighting caused concern among residents.
